{"tid":1154700,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"給愛犬取名「城管」，曼迷尋釁滋事被行政拘留10日。","createTime":"2019-05-14T12:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T13:15:06.000Z","uid":28938,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aa89fa7235a074239e82b48d527fef8a470e20ca","tid":1154700,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:49:40.000Z","msg":"安徽阜陽有狗主因為給愛犬取名「城管」、「協管」，並多次在朋友圈發佈相關消息，最終因涉尋釁滋事被行政拘留10日。<br />\n<br />\n阜陽市公安局潁州分局沙河路派出所昨日（13日）接報後，民警當即展開調查。該男子班某東被依法傳喚至派出所。經查，班某東生於1988年，主要依靠養狗賣狗維持生計，他表示給狗狗取名「城管」、「協管」，只是因為覺得好玩，「我不懂法（律），不知道這是違法的。」<br />\n<br />\n被警方傳喚後，他表示非常後悔，表示會將狗狗改名做「曼狗」、「曼狗二號」比較穩當。他最終因尋釁滋事，被警方行政拘留10日，並已送阜陽市拘留所執行。"},{"pid":"f0a111e10901f568f194f60a506c6917237bb20b","tid":1154700,"uid":131078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:55:58.000Z","msg":"Nineup 報<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afc8d64a36be0842f91756bcab8b3fa78d7e54d","tid":1154700,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:57:11.000Z","msg":"司馬蛇回晒塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af47a9265a819edd8a32c17d92c5afc4a2568878","tid":1154700,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df55666abde2bf9bf0ebe841a947a359d5992e91","tid":1154700,"uid":216021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166b5c806f3ecb5e5c558a7bec73451c3b5f55cf","tid":1154700,"uid":111814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:15:06.000Z","msg":"叫吸精瓶咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}